 <PERSON> Ruth </PERSON> <PERSON> Sinai </PERSON> covers international affairs for <ORGANIZATION> The </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION> in <LOCATION> Washington </LOCATION>.
