least $ 2 million at current bullion prices, Ms. <PERSON> Chan </PERSON> said. The gold was believed to have been the payroll for workers building the <LOCATION> Sault </LOCATION> Ste. Marie locks between lakes Superior and <LOCATION> Huron </LOCATION>.
