 state-run <ORGANIZATION> Banca </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Comerciale </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Italiana </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> SpA </ORGANIZATION>, <LOCATION> Italy </LOCATION>'s second largest bank. The <ORGANIZATION> Banca </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Commerciale </ORGANIZATION> bid is part of a complex restructuring plan that includes sale of Irving assets, several cost-cutting measures and a special dividend. The proposal still requires regulatory approval.
